statements.sql: select "networks".*, "terceros_networks"."customer_id" as "pivot_customer_id", "terceros_networks"."network_id" as "pivot_network_id", "terceros_networks"."padre_id" as "pivot_padre_id", "terceros_networks"."created_at" as "pivot_created_at", "terceros_networks"."updated_at" as "pivot_updated_at" from "networks" inner join "terceros_networks" on "networks"."id" = "terceros_networks"."network_id" where "networks"."deleted_at" is null and "terceros_networks"."customer_id" in ('26')

select "terceros"."id", "terceros"."nombres", "terceros"."apellidos", "terceros"."email" from "terceros" inner join "terceros_networks" on "terceros"."id" = "terceros_networks"."padre_id" where "terceros"."id" = '26' and "terceros_networks"."network_id" = '1'

select "permissions".*, "permission_role"."created_at" as "pivot_created_at", "permission_role"."updated_at" as "pivot_updated_at" from "permissions" inner join "permission_role" on "permission_role"."permission_id" = "permissions"."id" inner join "roles" on "roles"."id" = "permission_role"."role_id" where 0 = 1 or "roles"."level" < '0' group by "permissions"."id", "pivot_created_at", "pivot_updated_at"
